{"tid":2263944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽障男生被指襲警 市民作證指多名警察瞄頭揮棍打被告近十下","createTime":"2020-10-30T08:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T10:18:21.000Z","uid":56115,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed8548ffde24f3825b25dbaf4e8c3196d797610","tid":2263944,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"辯方今引述事發翌日被告的醫療報告，證實被告<span class=\"red\">左肋骨前方兩節骨折、右肋骨移位</span>。有市民今供稱，當日目擊多名警員<span class=\"red\">「瞄住」被告頭部</span>，揮警棍打被告近十下，他欲阻止不果，更因此被其他警員毆打。<br />\n<br />\n目擊事發經過的市民鄺（38歳）今供稱，當日由鵝頸橋回家，走到銅鑼灣地鐵站C出口外報紙攤位置，見被告被約四名警員用警棍由上而下揮打，「我好肯定警察係瞄住佢個頭嚟打⋯我下意識覺得會出事，所以就過去阻止。」鄺隨即被其他警員扯向後方制止，「俾佢打咗陣，同向我噴咗好多胡椒噴霧。」後來鄺與被告一同被帶到銅鑼灣地鐵站下層，然後前住北角警署，其間有警員向鄺指出，「頭先你要救嘅人就係呢個人。」"},{"pid":"555547d84de72b21184e2e88167ce58289344df9","tid":2263944,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:56:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/DK3PANXL2FDKHEBJ7ZY5IZMH2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FDK3PANXL2FDKHEBJ7ZY5IZMH2Q%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=7a7c35a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FDK3PANXL2FDKHEBJ7ZY5IZMH2Q%2F&h=e1811eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/DK3PANXL2FDKHEBJ7ZY5IZMH2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"bba27b41f630f94a7a0c36a455cd2436ac256ae7","tid":2263944,"uid":43062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線完全係慌你唔撚死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9782cdaabbaf882462a851b780c0510b3b54a16a","tid":2263944,"uid":354545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"打人班蓄牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class